orean" lang="ko" hreflang="ko" class="interlanguage-link-target">한국어</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-hi"><a href="https://hi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%88_%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE" title="भाषाई सापेक्षता – Hindi" lang="hi" hreflang="hi" class="interlanguage-link-target">हिन्दी</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-io"><a href="https://io.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hipotezo_di_Sapir-Whorf" title="Hipotezo di Sapir-Whorf – Ido" lang="io" hreflang="io" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ido</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-id"><a href="https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hipotesis_Sapir-Whorf" title="Hipotesis Sapir-Whorf – Indonesian" lang="id" hreflang="id" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bahasa Indonesia</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ia"><a href="https://ia.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypothese_de_Sapir-Whorf" title="Hypothese de Sapir-Whorf – Interlingua" lang="ia" hreflang="ia" class="interlanguage-link-target">Interlingua</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-is"><a href="https://is.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sapir_-_Whorf_tilg%C3%A1tan" title="Sapir - Whorf tilgátan – Icelandic" lang="is" hreflang="is" class="interlanguage-link-target">Íslenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-it"><a href="https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ipotesi_di_Sapir-Whorf" title="Ipotesi di Sapir-Whorf – Italian" lang="it" hreflang="it" class="interlanguage-link-target">Italiano</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-he"><a href="https://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%94%D7%99%D7%A4%D7%95%D7%AA%D7%96%D7%AA_%D7%A1%D7%A4%D7%99%D7%A8-%D7%95%D7%95%D7%A8%D7%A3" title="היפותזת ספיר-וורף – Hebrew" lang="he" hreflang="he" class="interlanguage-link-target">עברית</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kn"><a href="https://kn.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%B2%AD%E0%B2%BE%E0%B2%B7%E0%B2%BF%E0%B2%95_%E0%B2%B8%E0%B2%BE%E0%B2%AA%E0%B3%87%E0%B2%95%E0%B3%8D%E0%