irova-Whorfova hypotéza – Slovak" lang="sk" hreflang="sk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Slovenčina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sl"><a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sapir-Whorfova_hipoteza" title="Sapir-Whorfova hipoteza – Slovenian" lang="sl" hreflang="sl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Slovenščina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sr"><a href="https://sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B0%D0%BF%D0%B8%D1%80%E2%80%94%D0%92%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%84%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0_%D1%85%D0%B8%D0%BF%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%B0" title="Сапир—Ворфова хипотеза – Serbian" lang="sr" hreflang="sr" class="interlanguage-link-target">Српски / srpski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fi"><a href="https://fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sapirin%E2%80%93Whorfin_hypoteesi" title="Sapirin–Whorfin hypoteesi – Finnish" lang="fi" hreflang="fi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Suomi</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sv"><a href="https://sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sapir%E2%80%93Whorf-hypotesen" title="Sapir–Whorf-hypotesen – Swedish" lang="sv" hreflang="sv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Svenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tr"><a href="https://tr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sapir-Whorf_hipotezi" title="Sapir-Whorf hipotezi – Turkish" lang="tr" hreflang="tr" class="interlanguage-link-target">Türkçe</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%93%D1%96%D0%BF%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%B0_%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BF%D1%96%D1%80%D0%B0_%E2%80%94_%D0%92%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%84%D0%B0" title="Гіпотеза Сепіра — Ворфа – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gi%E1%BA%A3_thuy%E1%BA%BFt_Sapir-Whorf" title="Giả thuyết Sapir-Whorf – Vietnamese" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="https://zh.wi